# GlimmoraTeam — AI SOW Generator API

## Project Overview
FastAPI + MongoDB backend for the 10-Step Statement of Work (SOW) Wizard.
**Stack:** Python 3.11+, FastAPI, Motor (async MongoDB), Pydantic v2, JWT auth, pytest-asyncio.

