## Validation Rules (Wizard)
Always enforce these — never skip them:

| Code    | Rule |
|---------|------|
| WIZ-001 | Steps 0,1,2,5,7,8 must be complete before generation |
| WIZ-002 | Data Sensitivity Level has NO default — must be explicitly selected |
| WIZ-003 | Both Business Owner + Final Approver required |
| WIZ-004 | Industry "Other" requires free-text |
| WIZ-005 | Budget max ≥ min |
| WIZ-006 | Non-discrimination — HARD BLOCK, cannot be overridden |
| WIZ-007 | Personal data → privacy law selection required |
| WIZ-008 | Migration → technical detail required |
| WIZ-009 | UAT sign-off authority required |
| WIZ-010 | Business objectives need at least one measurable target |
| WIZ-011 | Browser + device matrix — at least one each |

