## Testing
- Framework: `pytest` + `pytest-asyncio`
- All test fixtures are in `tests/conftest.py`
- Run: `pytest tests/ -v`
- Unit tests (no DB): `pytest tests/test_wizard.py -k "confidence or hallucination" -v`

---

## Do NOT
- Do NOT use synchronous DB calls (no `pymongo` directly in routers/services).
- Do NOT return raw MongoDB `_id` (ObjectId) — always convert to string.
- Do NOT use `class Config` in Pydantic models — use `model_config = ConfigDict(...)`.
- Do NOT add new router prefixes outside of `/api/v1`.
- Do NOT hardcode secrets or connection strings — always use `settings.*`.
- Do NOT allow WIZ-006 (non-discrimination) to be bypassed under any circumstance.
